flowchart LR
    A[Push to main] --> B{Lint & Test}
    B -- fail --> X[Notify Slack]
    B -- pass --> C[Build image]
    C --> D[Push to ECR]
    D --> E{Env?}
    E -- staging --> F[Deploy to staging]
    E -- prod --> G[Manual approval]
    G --> H[Deploy to prod]
    F --> I[Run smoke tests]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Done]
